User accesses www.foobar.com → DNS (A record) → 8.8.8.8 → Server with:
- Nginx web server
- Application server
- Application code base
- MySQL database

Domain name: human-readable name pointing to IP
www → A record
Web server: handles HTTP and serves static files
Application server: runs application logic
Database: stores persistent data
Communication: HTTP/HTTPS

Issues:
- Single Point of Failure
- Downtime during maintenance
- Cannot scale with heavy traffic
